{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/", "destination": "/landing.html" },
    { "source": "/((?!landing.html).*)", "destination": "/index.html" }
  ],
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/assets/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        { "key": "Cache-Control", "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        { "key": "X-Content-Type-Options",    "value": "nosniff" },
        { "key": "X-Frame-Options",           "value": "DENY" },
        { "key": "X-XSS-Protection",          "value": "1; mode=block" },
        { "key": "Referrer-Policy",           "value": "strict-origin-when-cross-origin" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "outputDirectory": "dist",
  "installCommand": "npm install",
  "framework": "vite"
}
```

---

### What changed and why

| | Old | New |
|---|---|---|
| `/` | → React app | → `landing.html` ✅ |
| `/signup`, `/login`, etc. | → React app | → React app ✅ (unchanged) |

Only **one line added** at the top of rewrites. Everything else is identical to your current file.

